cs.LO, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.MA

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic-based synthesis approaches and decomposition of GR(1) games. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper presents a multi-agent robot gridworld example to demonstrate the application of the developed ideas. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with systems with complex behavior and coordination tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with reactive motion planning for robots. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also a possible category as the paper deals with coordination tasks in multi-agent systems.
